name: Voidwalker
blurb: 1P Puzzle/Exploration Portal-like game with groundbreaking new Spellcrafting system. For PC & Oculus w/ potential Hydra compatibility.

rewards.reward:
NOVICE
~~~
You are curious about Void magic, but would rather leave the hard research to the Academic types! 
~~~ For your interest, you will receive a heartfelt Thank You from Voidwalker's development team as well as access to the backers' only newsletter and backers' forums.

STUDENT
~~~
You have considered attending the Royal Arcane Academy, but you are a little unsure about taking classes from Dr. Agrippa... ~~~

All previous reward tiers plus a set of high resolution desktop wallpapers.

SHAMAN
~~~
Congratulations on your acceptance to the Royal Arcane Academy! ~~~
You will receive all previous reward tiers plus a DRM-free digital download of the game upon release (OR a Steam download code if possible), and a PDF of the game manual.
MAGE ~~~ 8 high resolution desktop wallpapers (one from each magical element), your name in the "Special Thanks" portion of our website, and all previous reward tiers.
SORCERER ~~~ Digital collection of high resolution concept art, one extra DRM-free digital download of the finished game (OR one extra Steam download code if possible) plus all previous reward tiers.
FIRE SHAMAN ~~~ EARLY ACCESS TO OUR BETA, Voidwalker mousepad, 1 postcard sized concept art print, and your name in our end credits. Plus all previous reward tiers.
WATER SORCERER ~~~ Physical DRM-free copy of the game on a thumbdrive, plus all previous reward tiers.
EARTHMAGE ~~~ PDF of Voidwalker's Art Book, plus 8 postcard sized concept art prints (one of those postcards will be a limited edition signed print!), plus all previous reward tiers.

AIR  TEMPEST ~~~ 1 Limited Edition 8x10 signed print of concept art, plus your thumbdrive containing your physical copy of the game is now going to be made of wood! You also now get 5 digital copies if the game (as opposed to 2). Plus all previous reward tiers.
ENTROPY MONK ~~~ All 8 Limited Edition 8x10 prints of concept art, plus a signed Voidwalker poster! Plus all previous reward tiers.

LIGHT CRUSADER ~~~ Boxed Collector's Edition of the game complete with ETCHED wooden thumbdrive containing your DRM-free copy of the game and a printed copy of the game manual. Plus all previous reward tiers (except the previously promised thumbdrive which is replaced by the Collector's Edition copy).

ENERGY PRIEST ~~~ Get your face in the game! We will hang a portrait or tapestry of you, your character, your company logo, etc somewhere in the game. PLUS a T-shirt signed by the whole development team, plus all previous reward tiers.

TANGIBLE MASTER ~~~ Work with our head writer and write an in-game book that will appear in Voidwalker and all of it's sequels! You also now get 8 digital copies of the game (as opposed to 5), plus a hardcover print of the Voidwalker art book, as well as all of the previous tiers.
INTANGIBLE MASTER ~~~ You will have an in-game room, shrine, or area built and dedicated specifically to you! Plus you now receive all 4 Posters, signed, and all previous reward tiers.

PROFESSOR DOCTOR ~~~ Did you know that our Level Designer is also a historical seamstress? She will custom tailor a set of Royal Arcane Academy robes specifically for you! (Includes robe and shirt). And what good is an outfit without the trusty Phylactory? We will send you also a figurine of this game character to help complete your outfit. You will also get to chat via Skype with the entire dev team, and receive a free digital copy of Super Tea Studio's next major game! You also now get 10 digital copies of the game (as opposed to 8). Plus all previous reward tiers.

VOIDWALKER ~~~ Our on-team seamstress will custom tailor a set of truly extravagant velvet Professor's robes for you from the Royal Arcane Academy. Handstitching and embroidered or appliqued runes are a guarantee! (Includes robe and shirt). You will also receive a plaque of appreciation from Super Tea Studios, as well as a copy of all of Super Tea Studios' games released within next 10 years! Plus all previous reward tiers.
